## 📊 What's Excellent

### 1. **Architecture & Type Safety** ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

- Full end-to-end type safety via tRPC
- Professional database schema with proper indexing
- Clean monorepo structure
- Decimal.js for financial precision (no floating-point errors)

### 2. **Innovative Features** ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

- **AI-powered screenshot parsing** - Unique differentiator
- **Multi-currency support** - Underserved market
- **Private asset tracking** - Competitors don't offer this
- **Real-time WebSocket updates** - Modern UX

