## ⚠️ What Needs Work

### 1. **Performance Issues** (Critical)

- **Portfolio loading:** 20-30 seconds for large portfolios
- **Root cause:** Sequential API calls with rate limiting
- **Fix time:** 30 minutes (see QUICK_IMPROVEMENTS.md)
- **Impact:** 80% improvement (3-5 seconds)

### 2. **Missing Features** (Important)

- **No portfolio analytics** - Users want charts showing gains/losses over time
- **Limited onboarding** - Users need guidance on first use
- **Fix time:** 2-3 weeks for analytics, 1 week for onboarding wizard

**Note:** Budgeting and detailed transaction tracking are intentionally out of scope for MVP. These are complex features requiring bank integrations and are planned for premium tiers.

### 3. **Testing** (Critical)

- **Current state:** Test suite broken
- **Coverage claim:** "93%" but cannot verify
- **Reality:** Only utility tests work
- **Fix time:** 1-2 weeks for comprehensive coverage

### 4. **User Experience** ✅ **SIGNIFICANTLY IMPROVED**

**Recent Improvements (Sep 2025):**

- ✅ **Onboarding wizard** - 4-step guided tour for new users
- ✅ **Professional empty states** - All pages have clear guidance
- ✅ **Enhanced notifications** - User-friendly error messages
- ✅ **Accessibility** - WCAG AA compliant (94/100 score)
- ✅ **Help system** - Floating help widget with searchable articles

**Remaining Polish:**

- ⚠️ Loading skeletons (1 hour)
- ⚠️ Complete toast migration (1 hour)
- ⚠️ Apply validation to all forms (2-3 hours)

