## 💰 Business Viability

### Target Market

✅ **Primary Target Audience:**

**Digital nomads and globally mobile individuals with $50k+ portfolios**

- Living/working across multiple countries
- Managing assets in multiple currencies
- Mix of crypto, stocks, real estate, and traditional investments
- Too small for wealth managers ($50k-500k range)
- Need portfolio visibility without complex bank integrations

✅ **Also well-positioned for:**

- International investors and expats
- Crypto + traditional asset holders
- Privacy-conscious users (self-hosted option)
- People with private assets (real estate, art, etc.)

❌ **NOT targeting:**

- Mass market US consumers (different needs, Mint/YNAB serve them well)
- Budget-focused users (out of scope)
- Users requiring automatic bank sync (global coverage is poor)

### Monetization Potential

```
Free Tier:     1 base currency, up to 10 holdings, manual entry
Pro Tier:      $9.99/mo - unlimited currencies/holdings, AI screenshot parsing
Premium Tier:  $19.99/mo - transaction tracking, bank statement parsing, tax reports
Enterprise:    $49.99/mo - multi-user, API access, white-label

Target: 1,000 paid users (70% Pro, 30% Premium) = $13k MRR (achievable in 6-9 months)
Digital nomad market: ~35 million globally, 5-10% have $50k+ portfolios = 1.75-3.5M addressable market
```

### Competitive Advantages

1. **Global-first design** - Built for multi-currency from day 1 (not bolted on)
2. **Screenshot AI** - Unique friction-reducer for manual data entry
3. **Private assets** - Track real estate, art, private equity (competitors ignore this)
4. **No bank dependency** - Works globally without region-locked Plaid/similar APIs
5. **Modern tech** - Faster, more reliable than legacy platforms
6. **Digital nomad focused** - Only product built specifically for globally mobile investors

